@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hleeyp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.75 - v0 + 0.14) / 0.53))
    tmp = 0.68
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v0 + 0.33 * v2 + 0.48)))
    v1 = (tmp + wp.abs((v1 + 0.61 / v0 + 0.49)))
    data[tid] = v0
